# Project Goal

Predict compiler stack layouts directly from stripped Borland x86 assembly:

```text
Raw ASM
   ↓

ML Model (LLM / GNN)

   ↓

Recovered Stack Layout

[ebp-4]  → local_var1
[ebp-8]  → buffer
esi      → cached_ptr
```

Target:

**Recover compiler allocation logic without debug symbols.**